    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥推行新规以刺激小企业发行更多债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/mexico-touts-new-stock-debt-rules-to-spark-more-issuance-by-smaller-firms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥政府和当地交易所的官员周四表示，允许墨西哥小公司简化发行股票和债券的新规定为当地证券市场的复苏铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/mexico-touts-new-stock-debt-rules-to-spark-more-issuance-by-smaller-firms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 00:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
